                      <strong>Framework Updates:</strong> Updates to Bootstrap and other dependencies
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <p>
                    Updates are delivered via email with detailed changelog and upgrade
                    instructions.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ 13 -->
            <div
              class="accordion-item border rounded-3 mb-3"
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-delay="300"
              data-aos-duration="1400"
            >
              <h3 class="accordion-header">
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed fw-semibold"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#support3"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="support3"
                >
                  What if I need custom development work?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div
                id="support3"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                data-bs-parent="#supportAccordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>We offer custom development services for additional requirements:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      <strong>Custom Features:</strong> Build specific functionality for your community
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <strong>Third-party Integrations:</strong> Connect with payment systems, management
                      software
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <strong>Design Customization:</strong> Major design changes beyond the included
                      themes
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Backend Development:</strong> Custom server-side functionality</li>
                    <li>
                      <strong>Migration Services:</strong> Help moving from your current website
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <p>Contact our team for a custom quote based on your specific requirements.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Still Have Questions -->
  <section
    class="py-5 text-center"
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);"
  >
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold text-white mb-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800">
            Still Have Questions?
          </h2>
          <p
            class="lead mb-4"
            style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-delay="200"
            data-aos-duration="800"
          >
            Can't find the answer you're looking for? Our support team is here to help you get
            started with your HOA website.
          </p>
          <div
            class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 flex-wrap"
            data-aos="fade-up"
            data-aos-delay="400"
            data-aos-duration="800"
          >
            <a href="mailto:support@example.com" class="btn btn-light btn-lg rounded-pill px-4">
              <i class="ri-mail-line me-2"></i>Contact Support
            </a>
            <a href={getPathPrefix('/')} class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg rounded-pill px-4">
              <i class="ri-eye-line me-2"></i>View Demo
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <small style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);">
              <i class="ri-time-line me-1"></i>
              Average response time: 24 hours
